Usage: sdwan.py template-device [OPTIONS]

  Display, Download, and Upload Device Templates.

    List templates to derive templateID for additional actions

  Example Command:

      sdwan.py template-device

      sdwan.py template-device --attached <templateId>

      sdwan.py template-device --clone <templateId> <model>

      sdwan.py template-device --config <templateId>

      sdwan.py template-device --csv <templateId>

      sdwan.py template-device --download <templateId> | all

      sdwan.py template-device --upload <file>

      sdwan.py template-device --tree <templateId>

      sdwan.py template-device --variable <templateId>

Options:
  --attached TEXT  Template to display attached devices
  --clone TEXT...  Clone Template to same or different Model
  --config TEXT    Template to display
  --csv TEXT       Template CSV Header
  --download TEXT  Template to download
  --upload TEXT    File to upload Template
  --tree TEXT      List templates and variables referenced
  --variable TEXT  List of variables required
  --help           Show this message and exit.
